Zajan is a excellent set up magi. He lasts for a while because he energizes at the end of his turn so he always has energy during my opponents turn.<br>
The fact that he starts with Nodj, Plith and Tap Roots. <br>
<br>
Yaki<br>
Yaki is where this deck starts to launch. Yaki is in there for full on attack. The fact that all of his cretures can attack twice for ultimate damage.<br>
<br>
Evil Evu<br>
Evil Evu is the man! Not only does he draw cards to get things out but his two creatures are attack creatures. I use the Dark Furok to remove two creatures at once. <br>
